Class SpaceObject

java.lang.Object
SpaceObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
Debris, Payload, RocketBody, Satellite, Unknown
public abstract class SpaceObject extends Object
Abstract class representing a general space object in orbit. This class provides common attributes and methods shared by debris and satellite objects.
